{"tid":421972,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯嘅冬天駛唔駛用雪櫃？","createTime":"2017-10-02T16:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T10:32:25.000Z","uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5d8b5b96b803411da0107392f29e7d46c33c0e20","tid":421972,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:20:38.000Z","msg":"香港一年四季都比較熱 所以大部分食物、嘢飲都要放雪櫃先唔易變壞<br />\n不過極地、寒冷地區嘅人又會點做？<br />\n（俄國首都莫斯科11月至3月平均高溫係1.5以下，平均低溫最低12度，都未計極端低溫）<br />\n<br />\n所以：<br />\n牛奶要4度以下=氣溫會結冰/室溫又有暖氣<br />\n=開暖氣+放雪櫃？<br />\n定冷暖氣調櫃？<br />\n<br />\n又例如啲要放冰格嘅嘢，例如冰鮮肉<br />\n係淨包好放冇暖氣嘅地方就ok?"},{"pid":"bd5288401a037ca97328830b6411804acd3d6321","tid":421972,"uid":86762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:40:19.000Z","msg":"其實冬天D肉放室外係冇問題<br />\n只不過冇乜人會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPS: 加拿大"},{"pid":"8ba4972beb0a6571dcf129078e9e041e2bd12385","tid":421972,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:47:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實冬天D肉放室外係冇問題<br />\n只不過冇乜人會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPS: 加拿大</blockquote><br />\n有冇試過放冇暖氣嘅室內為環保出一分力"},{"pid":"d2140bc3fa62bf3e75256f7458e5a93b17ac6d8b","tid":421972,"uid":76641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:49:27.000Z","msg":"冬天去過大陸北部，平均每日都0-2度，雪櫃係抆左制當普通櫃咁裝野食，我諗俄羅斯唔會差太遠，反正用唔著何苦哂電"},{"pid":"ebdc7b31fc824ace0b604a299b3b180bbfcb3506","tid":421972,"uid":128229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T17:12:01.000Z","msg":"班俄佬不嬲將d酒/食物就咁係出面雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟當年去俄國旅行都成日雪飲品"},{"pid":"8041e1b06b4caca302a7fd4885e36b20111e4cc0","tid":421972,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T18:05:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班俄佬不嬲將d酒/食物就咁係出面雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟當年去俄國旅行都成日雪飲品</blockquote><br />\n如果天氣太凍 又要保鮮又唔想食冰 有乜方法可以保持食物喺4度？"},{"pid":"8a7669c9901f3602c24661555fc6a747e4f5372e","tid":421972,"uid":26506,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T18:11:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冬天去過大陸北部，平均每日都0-2度，雪櫃係抆左制當普通櫃咁裝野食，我諗俄羅斯唔會差太遠，反正用唔著何苦哂電</blockquote><br />\n一海之隔九龍新界咁凍?"},{"pid":"dc1af51c8cc575fa40637e97b4a162bba210b446","tid":421972,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T18:16:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冬天去過大陸北部，平均每日都0-2度，雪櫃係抆左制當普通櫃咁裝野食，我諗俄羅斯唔會差太遠，反正用唔著何苦哂電</blockquote><br />\n大陸北方好似有集體供暖。室內唔會同室外一樣溫度"},{"pid":"046c468975efc3c67f823472ecb1b4e6be1c0b43","tid":421972,"uid":63925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T18:16:33.000Z","msg":"我係加拿大冬天都會將飲剩既湯成煲擺係後園室外<br />\n仲凍過雪櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c54ceff6ee796f7f94a921cb86dd2182ed060676","tid":421972,"uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T18:22:42.000Z","msg":"喺英國開party 之前<br />\n拎個容器裝水然後擺曬啲酒落去拎出室外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecfdeef6ea7a2f54c1969f1c31a6496b8c2f0342","tid":421972,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T18:31:12.000Z","msg":"野飲的確放出面<br />\n但野食照放雪櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d744f85b368ee0544f5224293b26ac48b995a9f","tid":421972,"uid":12557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T18:36:46.000Z","msg":"隻窗有內外兩層<br />\n冬天會將兩層中間d 位當雪櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09df95adadc36a840ebb97468b72ea303f3b1a05","tid":421972,"uid":10890,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:12:26.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;We want out beer cold, but not frozen&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ac6a79bc30b7cee53758948e2c0211717880e9","tid":421972,"uid":86762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:31:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實冬天D肉放室外係冇問題<br />\n只不過冇乜人會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPS: 加拿大</blockquote><br />\n有冇試過放冇暖氣嘅室內為環保出一分力</blockquote><br />\n痴撚線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冬天零下廿幾度唔開暖氣<br />\n我住緊呢頭呢幾晚已經跌到得番七八度<br />\n已經開緊暖氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a209f1980a3cf267755f4912f926bd79cd6d35","tid":421972,"uid":86762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:33:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係加拿大冬天都會將飲剩既湯成煲擺係後園室外<br />\n仲凍過雪櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n結埋冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7481520a5b33110b724d9e7c53be0b84744ef0","tid":421972,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T20:38:40.000Z","msg":"我地都試過幾箱啤酒放出街，唔洗阻住雪櫃又夠凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5620d547cab890de1a3ef61c877b67d65bf959c","tid":421972,"uid":76641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T02:42:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冬天去過大陸北部，平均每日都0-2度，雪櫃係抆左制當普通櫃咁裝野食，我諗俄羅斯唔會差太遠，反正用唔著何苦哂電</blockquote><br />\n大陸北方好似有集體供暖。室內唔會同室外一樣溫度</blockquote><br />\n我講緊紅磚瓦房個隻喎，佢地好多放雪櫃個位係無暖架"},{"pid":"0de158bb40cd6559607313c98ed180e414332fd6","tid":421972,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:16:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&ldquo;We want our beer cold, but not frozen&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class